item.description:
@Lazyness wrote:

reyx7:

It’s even funnier because datmaker can’t register textures.

Awe man… You’re not serious, are you? :eek: I’m screwed if it doesn’t! I use textures for items like my shields and masks. What other way is there to color something with a low amount of polygons and have it still register?

Topic creator - Don’t let poor criticism bring you down! Keep trying new things! If you keep at it and you have an artistic mindset, you’ll do great! Try making a sword from scratch or play around with primitives and what not.
